data.description: Discover the ease of one-level living in this practical ranch-style home in Hazelwood! The functional layout includes three bedrooms and a shared bathroom. Sit under the covered patio for outdoor relaxation, plant a garden in the raised beds, or explore other possibilities for the spacious, fenced yard. A one-car garage and a tool shed add multiple storage solutions. Situated on a dead-end street, across from a quiet park and Glendoveer Golf Course. New siding installed in 2018; new water heater in 2019.
